I mean...

114
00:05:30,400 --> 00:05:31,560
If...

115
00:05:32,280 --> 00:05:33,800
If one day,

116
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:34,440
you pass away,

117
00:05:34,440 --> 00:05:36,000
then, on the...

118
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:36,760
This thing...

119
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:38,520
On this thing,

