124
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,800
I haven't thought about it.

125
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:46,800
See?

126
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:50,800
You can engrave

127
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:52,000
your mom's name on the left,

128
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:52,600
and Mrs. Bai's name

129
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,000
on the right.

130
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,040
My name will be in the middle.

131
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:56,320
Can you do that?

132
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,080
Both of them!

133
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:59,600
Dad, you're such a playboy.

134
00:06:00,960 --> 00:06:03,120
How can you be that irresponsible?

135
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:04,280
If you've got both names on it,

136
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:05,240
then

137
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:07,400
