172
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:05,360
Son.

173
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,960
Come on, drink with me!

174
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:11,040
Cheers.

175
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,280
Thank you for supporting me.

176
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:14,040
