00:16:24,480 --> 00:16:26,800
I've lived a fulfilling and happy

290
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:28,680
life.

291
00:16:29,520 --> 00:16:30,560
I am fulfilled

292
00:16:30,560 --> 00:16:33,320
because I love my life.

293
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:37,280
